[The disease burden of malignant tumor in China, 1990 and 2010].

[Article in Chinese]

Liu Y(1), Liu J, Yin P, Liu S, Cai Y, You J, Zeng X, Wang L, Zhou M(2).

Author information:
(1)National Center for Chronic and Noncommunicable Disease Control and 
