[The disease burden of cardiovascular and circulatory diseases in China, 1990 
and 2010].

[Article in Chinese]

Liu J(1), Liu Y(1), Wang L(2), Yin P(1), Liu S(1), You J(1), Zeng X(1), Zhou 
