[Burden of disease attributable to ambient particulate matter pollution in 1990 
and 2010 in China].

[Article in Chinese]

Liu S(1), Zhou M(1), Wang L(1), Li Y(1), Liu Y(1), Liu J(1), You J(1), Yin P(2).

