OBJECTIVE: To assess the burden of disease attributable to ambient particulate 
matter pollution in 1990 and 2010 in China.
METHODS: On the basis of the results of the Global Burden of Diseases Study 2010 
(GBD 2010) for China's estimates, we used population attributable fractions 
(PAF) to examine the burden of disease (mortality and disability-adjusted life 
