The average life expectancy in Macau is ranking the second in the world, the 
consumption of fresh medicinal plants is a profound culture in Macau. The paper 
focus on the distribution of the antioxidant herbs, a comprehensive 
investigation and analysis the amount of the plant resources was carried out. 
